{"tid":1248391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好彩撞正暑假, 成班學生日日幫政府收工","createTime":"2019-06-21T12:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T13:24:40.000Z","uid":65790,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0cefc85436a21b3078f62f1683b4b5ecc1353ab6","tid":1248391,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"今日既抗爭行動係有效既, 只要有恆心, 日日出黎<br />\n不足兩星期政府一定跪<br />\n不受傷不流血不被捕"},{"pid":"62f2125233586dca3fd2d8089a711b59e12a8c51","tid":1248391,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:35:01.000Z","msg":"暑假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bb5eeef8c921e7906b1c61353e4be6edc540afc","tid":1248391,"uid":79182,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"大家記住 呢個係長期不合作運動<br />\n我地淨係圍住佢 唔好衝<br />\n啲犬清場 我地唔使硬碰<br />\n唔好送人頭俾佢<br />\n我地返去休息 抖足精神 第二日又嚟過<br />\n我地不斷做 搞亂個社會秩序<br />\n然後同政府談判先係辦法<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好死衝 無意思㗎 <br />\n我地做咩都唔合法<br />\n警犬做咩都有政府撐腰<br />\n我真係唔想再有義士犧牲<br />\n<br />\n我知有人會諗 叫咗咁多人出嚟<br />\n咩都唔做咁on9?<br />\n無錯我地係人多 但我地和平遊行又試過<br />\n衝擊佔領又試過 有用咩??<br />\n要贏 一定要試新方法<br />\n一於試吓不合作運動啦"},{"pid":"1a6a830f55fec80337d9b71e6ebfa1976c82d9f9","tid":1248391,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62f2125233586dca3fd2d8089a711b59e12a8c51","tid":1248391,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:35:01.000Z","msg":"暑假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:39:26.000Z","msg":"大學生sem break了"},{"pid":"54b919328347c51418fa8dfbbf2c7095d5efac98","tid":1248391,"uid":252178,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T12:40:54.000Z","msg":"朝早下午中學生+大學生<br />\n夜晚放工人士<br />\n通宵勇武+有心人士<br />\n要接力"},{"pid":"1f3885e830512af1312ae51ba3a184e7e17a2655","tid":1248391,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54b919328347c51418fa8dfbbf2c7095d5efac98","tid":